00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:46,910
 ♫ This noisy world, this lonely page ♫ 

647
00:42:46,910 --> 00:42:49,400
 ♫ Swept away by time ♫ 

648
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:52,521
 ♫ Eyes once looked far ♫ 

649
00:42:52,521 --> 00:42:56,880
 ♫ Now lost in the shift ♫ 

650
00:42:56,880 --> 00:43:00,120
 ♫ Autumn winds stir ♫ 

651
00:43:00,120 --> 00:43:02,600
 ♫ Smoke curls once more ♫ 

652
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:05,520
 ♫ Like clouds on the edge of sky ♫ 

653
00:43:05,520 --> 00:43:09,600
 ♫ Returning to my eyes ♫ 

654
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:12,881
 ♫ Looking back from the mountaintop ♫ 

655
00:43:12,881 --> 00:43:16,052
 ♫ Time lost its name ♫ 

656
00:43:16,052 --> 00:43:19,320
 ♫ Was it yesterday ♫ 

657
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:23,380
 ♫ Or tomorrow? ♫ 

658
00:43:23,380 --> 00:43:26,620
 ♫ The world has changed ♫ 

659
00:43:26,620 --> 00:43:29,020
 ♫ Beyond recall ♫ 

660
00:43:29,020 --> 00:43:31,140
 ♫ Time will fade ♫ 

661
00:43:31,140 --> 00:43:36,505
 ♫ All the words ever spoken ♫ 

662
00:43:36,505 --> 00:43:40,275
 ♫ Only this longing remains ♫ 

663
00:43:40,275 --> 00:43:46,380
 ♫ Crossing centuries and days ♫ 

664
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:49,772
 ♫ In a fleeting moment ♫ 

